data.description: Quick Closing Possible! * COMPLETELY UPDATED Premier 3/2 "Natchez" model in the desirable all-premier neighborhood of Royal Oak at Springdale. * Most furniture & accessories are available separately. * No expenses have been spared in the thorough upgrading of this beautiful home, beginning with the exterior. A PAVED DRIVE & WALKWAY along with all-new Professional Hardscaping & Landscape Lighting make for tremendous Curb Appeal, while the NEW ROOF (2022) & NEW HVAC (2023) provide peace of mind. * Inside, a tiled Foyer welcomes you into the OPEN Kitchen/Living/Dining area. The spacious kitchen has been remodeled to include new QUARTZ countertops with designer TILE BACKSPLASH; large Coffee/Wine Bar; new Stainless Appliance package, including a GAS STOVE & DOUBLE OVEN with built-in air fryer; as well as a RANGE HOOD, Custom Cabinetry, and moveable ISLAND with large pull-outs (ideal for small appliances) & double-drawers for maximum storage. The PANTRY CLOSET comes equipped with a sliding glass barn door, custom shelving & electric – Must See! * Ten-foot VOLUME CEILINGS add to the overall roominess of this OPEN CONCEPT floor plan, with 12-foot tray ceilings in the Great Room & Master Suite. Low-maintenance ENGINEERED HARDWOOD & TILE flooring throughout the home (NO CARPET) provides continuity with neutral colors that will coordinate with any decor style; while the PLANTATION SHUTTERS add a touch of elegance to every room. * A generous Screened Lanai is accessible from the Living/Dining Area and provides an ideal space for relaxation or outdoor dining – not to mention, the OVERSIZED LOT offers ample ROOM FOR A LARGE POOL & SPA or future expansion (Pool sketches provided upon request). * The Master Suite is privately located in the back of the home, and features two WALK-IN CLOSETS as well as an En-Suite Bathroom with Tiled Walk-In Shower, Garden Tub, & Dual-Sink Vanity. * Bedrooms 2 & 3 and the Guest Bathroom are conveniently located on the opposite side of the home, behind a Pocket Door. Both guest bedrooms are roomy and feature Tall Ceilings & Full-Sized Closets, while the front bedroom (currently used as an office / hobby room) contains a desk, shelving & mobile workstation, which are available separately. * The Laundry Room comes with added Upper Cabinets and a new Utility Sink; while the nearly 750-square-foot 2-Car + Golf Car Garage has enough room for all of your vehicle & storage needs. * LOW BOND BALANCE of only $4,047.48. * Close to Nancy Lopez Country Club and Championship Golf Course, Mulberry Regional Recreation Center, VA Administration, First Responders Recreation Center, Shopping, Restaurants, and More. PLEASE WATCH OUR VIDEO OF THIS SPECTACULAR PREMIER HOME, and CALL TODAY for your Private Showing or Virtual Tour!
